            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44201229">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">遣聂昌、耿南仲、陈过庭出割两河地，民坚守不奉召，凡累月，止得石州。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-22 19:41</span>
                  
                </p>
